delivers pure sophistication with everyday comfort.","fabricType":"Wash & Wear","color":"Royal White","colorHex":"#ffffff","images":["https://res.cloudinary.com/emanthread/image/upload/v1780137603/emaan-threads/products/nauhj7nmrkllbdilzugq.jpg","https://res.cloudinary.com/emanthread/image/upload/v1780137632/emaan-threads/products/fkwco9ay18uflu3nf9wp.jpg","https://res.cloudinary.com/emanthread/image/upload/v1780137658/emaan-threads/products/ysfmyticdwbafqegypog.jpg"],"imageLabels":[],"videoUrl":"$undefined","tags":["Summer","All Season","Wedding","Eid","Premium","Festive"],"badge":"Limited","inStock":true,"stockQuantity":50,"lowStockThreshold":5,"sku":"SKU: ET-SD-WW-WHITE-011","metaTitle":"White Cotton Kurta Shalwar for Men","metaDescription":"white kurta shalwar for men. Crisp white color, breathable  fabric, premium stitching, and elegant styling for Eid, Jummah, and formal wear.","rating":5,"reviewCount":1},{"id":"cmps7nu7b0004l204mzptnd2n","name":"Stone","slug":"stone-off-white-cotton-kurta-shalwar","price":4999,"originalPrice":6500,"description":"Stone Off White cotton kurta shalwar with a soft elegant tone, premium stitching, and comfortable formal appeal.","longDescription":"The Stone Off White kurta shalwar brings a soft and graceful look to traditional menswear. Made from breathable cotton fabric, it offers lasting comfort, smooth wear, and easy styling. The off white shade gives the outfit a refined premium appearance, making it suitable for Eid, weddings, Jummah, family gatherings, daytime events, and formal occasions. Designed with a classic collar, button placket, full sleeves, neat stitching, and relaxed trouser, this suit is ideal for men who prefer subtle elegance.","fabricType":"Wash & Wear","color":"Off White","colorHex":"#e0d6ca","images":["https://res.cloudinary.com/emanthread/image/upload/v1780137398/emaan-threads/products/o4qrbwi3sbki9eamx9ae.jpg","https://res.cloudinary.com/emanthread/image/upload/v1780137420/emaan-threads/products/gncap68fighxidikcmg8.jpg","https://res.cloudinary.com/emanthread/image/upload/v1780137442/emaan-threads/products/xlsqy4fxbrhwk6msiehb.jpg"],"imageLabels":[],"videoUrl":"$undefined","tags":["Summer","Premium","Budget","Casual","Wedding","Eid","Festive"],"badge":"Featured","inStock":true,"stockQuantity":120,"lowStockThreshold":5,"sku":"ET-ST-CT-OFFWHT-010","metaTitle":"Stone Off White Cotton Kurta Shalwar","metaDescription":"Buy Stone Off White cotton kurta shalwar for men. Soft premium shade, breathable cotton, elegant stitching, and refined style for Eid and formal wear.","rating":"$undefined","reviewCount":0},{"id":"cmps7ms9n0001jr0459cs8o9q","name":"Stone","slug":"stone-ivory-cream-cotton-kurta-shalwar","price":4999,"originalPrice":7999,"description":"Stone Ivory Cream cotton kurta shalwar with a warm premium tone, graceful look, and comfortable all-day fit.","longDescription":"The Stone Ivory Cream kurta shalwar is made for men who prefer a warm, soft, and elegant traditional style. Crafted from comfortable cotton fabric, it provides breathable wear, smooth texture, and lasting comfort. The ivory cream shade gives the suit a luxurious daytime appeal, making it perfect for Eid, Jummah, weddings, family gatherings, festive events, and premium casual styling. Finished with a classic collar, button placket, full sleeves, neat stitching, and relaxed trouser, this outfit delivers timeless elegance with a soft modern finish.","fabricType":"Wash & Wear","color":"Ivory Cream","colorHex":"#fff5d9","images":["https://res.cloudinary.com/emanthread/image/upload/v1780136993/emaan-threads/products/rksn2nu6xxayuzo2jcwq.jpg","https://res.cloudinary.com/emanthread/image/upload/v1780137003/emaan-threads/products/xa6ceu3lfvg0tysfu28y.jpg","https://res.cloudinary.com/emanthread/image/upload/v1780137019/emaan-threads/products/dcqzvmj7uhhja92uw43c.jpg"],"imageLabels":[],"videoUrl":"$undefined","tags":["All Season","Summer","Premium","Eid","Wedding","Casual"],"badge":"Limited","inStock":true,"stockQuantity":10,"lowStockThreshold":5,"sku":"ET-ST-CT-IVORY-011","metaTitle":"Stone Ivory Cream Cotton Kurta Shalwar","metaDescription":"Shop Stone Ivory Cream cotton kurta shalwar for men. Warm elegant shade, breathable comfort, premium stitching, and refined style for Eid and festive wear.","rating":"$undefined","reviewCount":0},{"id":"cmps7lkqg0031jw04v6ulsola","name":"Stone","slug":"stone-white-cotton-kurta-shalwar","price":4999,"originalPrice":6499,"description":"Stone White cotton kurta shalwar with a crisp clean look, premium finish, and graceful traditional style.","longDescription":"The Stone White kurta shalwar is designed for men who prefer a fresh, clean, and timeless traditional outfit. Crafted from comfortable cotton fabric, it offers breathable wear, softness, and a refined appearance. The white shade gives the suit a graceful and polished look, ideal for Jummah, Eid, religious gatherings, daytime events, family occasions, and formal wear. Finished with a classic collar, button placket, full sleeves, neat stitching, and relaxed trouser, this suit delivers pure elegance with everyday comfort.","fabricType":"Wash & Wear","color":"White","colorHex":"#ffffff","images":["https://res.cloudinary.com/emanthread/image/upload/v1780137181/emaan-threads/products/i5tu5tmi7uby0tlywgmd.jpg","https://res.cloudinary.com/emanthread/image/upload/v1780137250/emaan-threads/products/czwgqyepjywyogfpmr42.jpg","https://res.cloudinary.com/emanthread/image/upload/v1780137269/emaan-threads/products/oilqg0rxm4mo2wzqnkqo.jpg"],"imageLabels":[],"videoUrl":"$undefined","tags":["Winter","Linen","Wedding","Premium","Eid"],"badge":"Featured","inStock":true,"stockQuantity":40,"lowStockThreshold":5,"sku":"ET-ST-CT-WHITE-009","metaTitle":"Stone White Cotton Kurta Shalwar for Men","metaDescription":"Shop Stone White cotton kurta shalwar for men. Crisp premium look, breathable fabric, elegant fit, and graceful style for Eid, Jummah, and formal wear.","rating":"$undefined","reviewCount":0},{